{"tid":764804,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【修法後首例】德國政府投票表決　否決中資收購精密機械商","createTime":"2018-08-02T09:06:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-02T22:58:36.000Z","uid":147314,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cecf2690c20a3675c6ba7d7c4e8486a3db67c815","tid":764804,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T09:06:37.000Z","msg":"修法後首例！ 德國政府否決中資收購精密機械商<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/business/page/800/2018/08/01/phpoPghEV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fbusiness%2Fpage%2F800%2F2018%2F08%2F01%2FphpoPghEV.jpg&h=990e83af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕繼美、英、加拿大等國之後，德國也加入阻止中資收購國內企業的行列。《彭博》引述知情人士報導，指德國梅克爾內閣今（1）日投票表決的方式，否決了中企煙台台海集團對德國精密機械製造商Leifeld Metal Spinning的收購案。這也是德國在去年修法後，首次否決中資收購案。<br />\n<br />\n據報導，<span style=\"color: red;\">雖然煙台台海集團已經在最後一刻表示將撤回對Leifeld的收購案，但德國政府仍採取這項預防措施。德國經濟部認為，該收購案將引發「國安問題」</span>，因此否決；Leifeld是德國汽車、太空、核子工業的精密金屬生產商。<br />\n<br />\n德國經濟部也考慮進一步收緊歐盟以外國家的投資規定。<br />\n<br />\n德國現行法律規定，外國企業若有意取得國防、資訊安全相關企業25％以上股權，須經過德國經濟部審核；上週德國經濟部表示，可能會尋求降低25%的股權審查門檻。<br />\n<br />\n過去中企高調收購德國企業引發反彈，2016年，中資美的集團收購德國機器人大廠庫卡（Kuka），引發德國輿論，是促使德國修法的主因。此外，先前在美國反對下，中資福建宏芯基金對德國半導體設備廠愛思強（Aixtron）收購案也破局。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2506423\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2506423&d=x5BhJw%2Fjm72IKdSWcJudsV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=715e03d3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2506423&h=cf5d1ae7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2506423</a>"},{"pid":"e1c707e2f15221c096ca6b48d11eceb3edc5ba21","tid":764804,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T09:09:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d080f1925ad79ff7ee05c59135927c044b4328d","tid":764804,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T09:17:23.000Z","msg":"平治都比支那人買咗啦！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n工業機械手臂又比支那人買咗！"},{"pid":"4a73337efb76829150d3f8577b05d786206a77ed","tid":764804,"uid":147314,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"3d080f1925ad79ff7ee05c59135927c044b4328d","tid":764804,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T09:17:23.000Z","msg":"平治都比支那人買咗啦！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n工業機械手臂又比支那人買咗！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T09:54:41.000Z","msg":"Benz ? 吉利做咗佢母企 Daimler 10%都無既大股東，<br />\n俾佢做水喉 only，無得話事"},{"pid":"a465392864bcaf1307bd2848438c633928fe0f56","tid":764804,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T10:06:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4604e8f53e0f0c485ea5c9ffaf7f7cd1028875ff","tid":764804,"uid":147314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3d080f1925ad79ff7ee05c59135927c044b4328d","tid":764804,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T09:17:23.000Z","msg":"平治都比支那人買咗啦！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n工業機械手臂又比支那人買咗！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T10:11:56.000Z","msg":"是否影響Daimler集團未來營運決策？<br />\n<br />\n不過，<span style=\"color: red;\">這並不意味未來吉利能主導Daimler集團的經營決策方向（事實上，未來吉利能否取得一席董事都存在不確定性）</span>，對Daimler集團這類股權高度分散的上市公司而言，事實上是沒有所謂「最大老闆」，如果一定要指定一個的話，暫時只能說是董事會主席Dieter Zetsche博士。在德國政府的鼓勵下，身為德國汽車工業重要火車頭的Daimler集團很早就以專業經理人負責日常營運，2008年金融危機以後，為了保證管理層擁有的決策權、並避免被其他企業收購，Daimler集團在股權結構上就進行了精心設計，加之公司經營業績良好，大股東（包括德國地方政府）也沒有出售股權的意願，這才是吉利不得不退而求其次在二級市場收購Daimler股權的根本原因。<br />\n<br />\n其實不只是Daimler集團，許多跨國汽車巨頭也都設計了「同股不同權」的機制（股權和投票權不是一回事），最大程度保障了經營團隊的控制權：例如豐田章男只擁有豐田公司2%的股份，但卻擁有20%的投票權，Ford家族只有Ford汽車集團6%的股份卻控制著40%的投票權。按照德國的法律規定，股東擁有超過75%的投票股權時才能完全掌握企業，真正成為這家企業的「大老闆」，所以<span style=\"color: red;\">吉利不僅目前無法成為Daimler集團的老闆，而且事實上今後也是不可能的。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=370391\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D370391&d=x5BhJw%2Fjm72IKdSWcJudsV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=35317fb5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D370391&h=abfd628e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=370391</a>"},{"pid":"f8d64779ecc3f90acc9ed5a0e2a1eb844bf7d45b","tid":764804,"uid":147314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T10:27:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">中國作為全球規模最大的汽車生產國，卻至今仍沒法生產符合現代汽車要求的引擎。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nC觀點: 施永青<br />\n內地民眾不了解中美差距<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/column/新聞/內地民眾不了解中美差距-124251\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fcolumn%2F%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E6%B0%91%E7%9C%BE%E4%B8%8D%E4%BA%86%E8%A7%A3%E4%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E5%B7%AE%E8%B7%9D-124251&d=x5BhJw%2Fjm72IKdSWcJudsV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=27ddea46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/column/新聞/內地民眾不了解中美差距-124251</a>"},{"pid":"5e3c02a4cb11bb9d628d0dc7b2ab018e4f643593","tid":764804,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T10:29:14.000Z","msg":"法西斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ced13ba9cdc079b33cbdc97a4c133e34ff3b2346","tid":764804,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T10:37:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56909c8aa9d21a3f18bcc9859e8dbc3a701644c4","tid":764804,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T10:39:00.000Z","msg":"被否決，又贏"},{"pid":"4689f015c426abab02a1e0a1863a245b28e25227","tid":764804,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T11:55:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"489fd29b122b63f33be9ad22532b8431d4bc3286","tid":764804,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a73337efb76829150d3f8577b05d786206a77ed","tid":764804,"uid":147314,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"3d080f1925ad79ff7ee05c59135927c044b4328d","tid":764804,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T09:17:23.000Z","msg":"平治都比支那人買咗啦！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n工業機械手臂又比支那人買咗！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T09:54:41.000Z","msg":"Benz ? 吉利做咗佢母企 Daimler 10%都無既大股東，<br />\n俾佢做水喉 only，無得話事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T22:54:20.000Z","msg":"噉都好D"},{"pid":"7caaf1222acb4489b07b84daddcc136c334a886b","tid":764804,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T22:58:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 陰公豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}